author: scheu
msg: Committer, Code, Design, Test: Rich Scheuerle
Issue Originally Discovered By: Tim Mitchell (IBM)
The attachment order in an incoming message is not preserved when written.
This can cause problems for applications that have a dependency on the attachment order.
The attachment order is now preserved and there a validation test is provided.
